134
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:16,068
Menurut prakiraan cuaca, salju akan turun.

135
00:10:16,188 --> 00:10:19,588
Dia pasti mengira membawa mobil akan berbahaya.

136
00:10:20,654 --> 00:10:22,555
Masahiko!

137
00:10:23,453 --> 00:10:25,287
Masahiko!

138
00:10:31,154 --> 00:10:32,454
Mungkinkah?

139
00:10:35,554 --> 00:10:36,587
Itu!

140
00:10:49,889 --> 00:10:52,857
