153
00:11:44,041 --> 00:11:48,141
Gundukan salju tinggi di atas sisi gunung yang teduh.

154
00:11:48,373 --> 00:11:50,640
Kau benar, tapi...

155
00:11:53,173 --> 00:11:55,041
