200
00:15:27,340 --> 00:15:29,373
-Apa? -Apa?

201
00:15:29,574 --> 00:15:33,208
Tunggu! Tidak ada tanda-tanda jebakan di TKP!

202
00:15:33,574 --> 00:15:38,108
