224
00:17:02,941 --> 00:17:06,742
-Conan! -Wajahmu masih bersalju.

225
00:17:08,373 --> 00:17:13,573
-Ayumi, kau tidak mau makan? -Aku mencium bawang putih.

226
00:17:14,540 --> 00:17:17,953
