228
00:17:20,874 --> 00:17:23,775
Aku lapar sekali.

229
00:17:24,307 --> 00:17:26,921
Saat Genta diam-diam memakan es krimnya,

230
00:17:27,041 --> 00:17:30,053
pelaku sedang membekukan seloyang air di dalam freezer

231
00:17:30,173 --> 00:17:33,173
untuk membuat lempengan es.

232
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:39,640
